strings: <voice_0x01001119><se_def>Economy: Carrie is coming from here. Hurry and get it!
<voice_0x0100111A><se_def>Economy: Don't miss your chance to teach them how to honor your brothers and sisters!
<voice_0x0100111B><se_high>Install on PC: By the way! How can you come to believe that you won't show up?
<voice_0x0100111C><se_high>Install on PC: If you've got money, you have to work hard!
<voice_0x0100111D><se_high>Install on PC: You need money, you want a wedding, I want good wishes...
